plot function

Source: R/plot.ineqx.R
plot.ineqx.Rd

[...]

# S3 method for ineqx
plot(
  ineqx.out,
  type,
  yint = 1,
  xlab = NULL,
  ylab = NULL,
  llab = NULL,
  titl = NULL,
  xlim = NULL,
  hline = F,
  se = F,
  lowess = F,
  legend = T,
  sav = F
)

Arguments

ineqx.out

ineqx.out object from ineqx()
type

dMuSigma2|dB|dW|dD|dO|dT
yint

1 or 2. 1: ..., 2: ...
sav

Value

Returns a ggplot2 object

Author

Benjamin Rosche <benjamin.rosche@gmail.com>
